sub_title: Student at Leiden University & TU Delft - MSc Industrial Ecology
summary: Chemical Engineer and Biologist from the University of Andes in Bogotá, with interests in sustainability and innovation of products and processes to make them a best fit for the consumer and the environment. Proficient in English and French. Knowledge in industrial processes, systems thinking and data analysis. Easily adaptable with skills in Microsoft Excel, leadership, teamwork, time management and organization.
